## Ionic Framework

Ionic needs no introduction, it is an HTML5 Mobile Framework for building, cross-platform hybrid native apps with HTML, JavaScript, and CSS.

2015 is a important for Ionic as they will slowly move from a simple HTML5 hybrid framework to a whole galaxy of tools to create hybrid apps.

### People to follow:

* [Max Lynch](https://twitter.com/maxlynch)
* [Andrew Joslin](https://twitter.com/andrewtjoslin)
* [Adam Bradley](https://twitter.com/adamdbradley)

